I'll take you to the guest room.

23
00:02:52,390 --> 00:02:53,480
I want to watch over him.

24
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,320
That's fine.

25
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:05,080
Okay. I'm leaving now.

